      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Even after staying in the hospital for 5 months and going through 7 months of physical therapy, Krogmeier still has a long way to go on the path to recovery. He says his voice has never been the same. Walking unassisted isn’t possible, either, and even then the man claims to “fall over a lot.” Doctors still aren’t sure he will ever fully recover, but Krogmeier sounds hopeful. What keeps driving him forward is the chance to show off his classic vehicles at car shows. He and his wife say they usually attend about 50 shows a year, something they hope to keep doing."
